com.broadcom.bt.le.api
Class BleConstants

java.lang.Object
  com.broadcom.bt.le.api.BleConstants

public class BleConstants
extends java.lang.Object

Contains a collection of GATT related constants used by Bluetooth Low Energy profiles and services. This is a purely static class containing the constant definitions.
